room_title: Escape room "Mystery at the Manor" by Two Trees Escape in Ventura
room_address: 2855 Johnson Dr Unit D Ventura, CA 93003
room_description: Eight guests from dueling nations were invited to a secluded island manor by Mr. Peabody, a wealthy benefactor orchestrating a peace treaty and donating his treasured Peace Diamond. Suddenly, Mr. Peabody is found dead, and now everybody is a suspect. Solve the mystery before the murderer strikes again!
